{
  "chapter": 50,
  "chapter_summary": "第五十回 海上飘。芮玮在叶青的帮助下乘长艇逃离魔鬼岛，叶青安排航海手驾船送行。然而叶士谋发现后残忍地射杀了航海手和叶青（三箭穿心）。芮玮将重伤的叶青救上船，简怀萱和呼哈娜在舱外划船。叶青伤势危急，芮玮取出药包中的金创药粉和灵丹为其疗伤。入夜风暴来袭，船身剧烈摇晃。芮玮无法出舱（伏在叶青身上防止伤口裂开），简怀萱爬上桅杆割断帆索，但桅杆断裂，她随桅杆坠入大海失踪。风暴过后，叶青苏醒但体力虚弱，简怀萱已无踪影，众人悲痛不已。长艇在海上漂流五日。第六日，一位轻功绝世的葛袍老者欧阳龙年踏木板而来，邀众人登上他的大船。其子欧阳波骄横无礼。芮玮询问简怀萱下落，欧阳波称曾救起一名女子但她又跳回海中。芮玮不信，叶青也质疑此事。此时船舱中走出一位神秘老太婆，道破欧阳龙年四十年前的海龙王匪号，暗示与其有旧。欧阳波对老太婆无礼，老太婆揭其兄惨死旧事警告欧阳龙年。欧阳波恼怒欲与芮玮动手，老太婆冷言讥讽。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_ye_qing",
      "text": "谢谢你，谢谢你……",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 2,
      "line_end": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "叶青",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你们快上船吧。",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "叶青",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "他是本岛最有名的航海手，有他在这艘长艇上，定可安然渡过大海回归中原，因为他忠厚老实，我已吩咐一定要送你们回去，你们放心好了。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 13
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_ye_qing",
      "text": "你帮咱们会不会给令尊发觉？",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "叶青",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "不会，不会，就是发觉，我是他女儿，不会对我太大的责罚。你们快上船，迟了有变。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 18,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_huai_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "简怀萱",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是大哥来了吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 23
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "叶青",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你我还能再见吧？",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 26
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_ye_qing",
      "text": "我不知道，你要来到中原，咱们或许能相见，魔鬼凫我是再也不来了！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 31
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_da_zhuang_han",
      "speaker_name": "高大壮汉",
      "listener": "char_ye_qing",
      "text": "郡主快回去免被岛主发觉。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_ye_shi_mou",
      "text": "来得好！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 47
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_ye_shi_mou",
      "text": "叶士谋，你好狠，俗云虎毒不食子，你竟连禽兽不如，亲生女儿也忍心杀害！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 59
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_shi_mou",
      "speaker_name": "叶士谋",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "船夫已死，姓芮的！看你还能逃离本岛主的掌心？",
      "tone": "狂笑",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_huai_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "简怀萱",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "大哥，青姐能救不？",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 71
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_jian_huai_xuan",
      "text": "一定能救！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_jian_huai_xuan",
      "text": "你们会不会划船？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "没有人划船，咱们不久又要重落叶士谋的掌心中！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 81
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_ha_na",
      "speaker_name": "呼哈娜",
      "listener": "char_jian_huai_xuan",
      "text": "咱划划。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 87
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_ha_na",
      "speaker_name": "呼哈娜",
      "listener": "char_jian_huai_xuan",
      "text": "不对！不对！向那边划。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_huai_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "简怀萱",
      "listener": "char_hu_ha_na",
      "text": "这位姐姐尊姓大名啊？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 105
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_ha_na",
      "speaker_name": "呼哈娜",
      "listener": "char_jian_huai_xuan",
      "text": "姓呼叫哈娜，你呢！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_huai_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "简怀萱",
      "listener": "char_hu_ha_na",
      "text": "我姓简名怀萱，你不是中原人氏吧？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 110,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_ha_na",
      "speaker_name": "呼哈娜",
      "listener": "char_jian_huai_xuan",
      "text": "啊！简召舞是你大哥？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_ha_na",
      "speaker_name": "呼哈娜",
      "listener": "char_jian_huai_xuan",
      "text": "刚才那阵风刮得好奇怪，看样子天快变了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 115
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_huai_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "简怀萱",
      "listener": "char_hu_ha_na",
      "text": "你认识简召舞？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 120
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_ha_na",
      "speaker_name": "呼哈娜",
      "listener": "char_jian_huai_xuan",
      "text": "认识，早就认识了，他到咱们国家去，屡次和父王商量，想向父王借兵攻打中原边际名将高大将军，我真想不透他是中原宰相之子，为何要借兵打起自己人来？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 123
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_ha_na",
      "speaker_name": "呼哈娜",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "快把住舵！快把住舵……",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_huai_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "简怀萱",
      "listener": "char_hu_ha_na",
      "text": "不行！不行！我……我……站不住……",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_huai_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "简怀萱",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "怎么办？怎么办？",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_jian_huai_xuan",
      "text": "萱妹，下帆！萱妹下帆！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 162
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_ha_na",
      "speaker_name": "呼哈娜",
      "listener": "char_jian_huai_xuan",
      "text": "对啦！快下帆，快下帆……",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "叶青",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "好了，只是全身没力。",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 214
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_ye_qing",
      "text": "令尊太狠心了，这三箭绝不容情，现在虽然治好，但你流血过多，一时体力无法完全恢复，至少养息一月。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 219
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "叶青",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "大哥，你又救了我一命……",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 222,
      "line_end": 222
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_ye_qing",
      "text": "昨夜好大的风浪，我真怕你伤口震得裂开，只好伏在你身上没教它裂开。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 225
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "叶青",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "什么事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_hu_ha_na",
      "text": "她呢？她呢？……",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 234,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_ha_na",
      "speaker_name": "呼哈娜",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "谁啊？谁啊？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_hu_ha_na",
      "text": "简怀萱不见于！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 238,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_ha_na",
      "speaker_name": "呼哈娜",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "我最后见她爬在顶上……",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 240
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_ha_na",
      "speaker_name": "呼哈娜",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_long_nian",
      "text": "喂，老先生，你是不是神仙？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 304,
      "line_end": 304
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_hu_ha_na",
      "text": "不是，这位老先生轻功甚高，借着木板在海上逍遥。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 308,
      "line_end": 309
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_ha_na",
      "speaker_name": "呼哈娜",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_long_nian",
      "text": "虽不是神仙，也是神仙啦。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 312,
      "line_end": 312
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_long_nian",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳龙年",
      "listener": "char_hu_ha_na",
      "text": "怎么又是神仙啦？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 314,
      "line_end": 314
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_ha_na",
      "speaker_name": "呼哈娜",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_long_nian",
      "text": "快活神仙啊！",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 316,
      "line_end": 316
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_long_nian",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳龙年",
      "listener": "char_hu_ha_na",
      "text": "不错，我在此邀游海上确实快活似神仙啊！我的船来接我啦。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 318,
      "line_end": 320
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_long_nian",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳龙年",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "请上大船。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 326,
      "line_end": 326
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_long_nian",
      "text": "多谢老先生美意。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 328,
      "line_end": 328
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_bo",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳波",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_long_nian",
      "text": "爹，有何发现？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 332,
      "line_end": 333
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_long_nian",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳龙年",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_bo",
      "text": "老样。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 336,
      "line_end": 336
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_long_nian",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳龙年",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "快上来吧！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 340,
      "line_end": 340
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_ye_qing",
      "text": "伏在我肩上。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 342,
      "line_end": 342
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_ye_qing",
      "text": "抱紧！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 346,
      "line_end": 346
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_long_nian",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳龙年",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "小伙子，轻功不错啊。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 350,
      "line_end": 350
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_hu_ha_na",
      "text": "你怕不怕？",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 352,
      "line_end": 352
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_ha_na",
      "speaker_name": "呼哈娜",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "不怕！",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 356,
      "line_end": 356
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_hu_ha_na",
      "text": "不怕就好！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 356,
      "line_end": 356
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_long_nian",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳龙年",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "小伙子，你很聪明。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 358,
      "line_end": 359
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_long_nian",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳龙年",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_bo",
      "text": "波儿，你和这位大哥亲近亲近。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 366,
      "line_end": 366
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_bo",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳波",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_long_nian",
      "text": "他们也是遭到大风暴的灾难的人吗？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 368,
      "line_end": 368
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_bo",
      "text": "兄台尊姓？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 370,
      "line_end": 371
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_bo",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳波",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "复姓欧阳，咱们这船留不得闲人，你们到了陆地就请快快上岸。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 374,
      "line_end": 375
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_bo",
      "text": "敝姓芮名玮，多有打扰，在下一事相问，能见告否？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 378,
      "line_end": 379
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_bo",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳波",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "什么事？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 382,
      "line_end": 382
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_bo",
      "text": "听兄台说好像救了数起灾难人。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 388,
      "line_end": 388
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_long_nian",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳龙年",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "连着你们共是第三次啦。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 390,
      "line_end": 391
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_bo",
      "text": "前两次中有没有位单身姑娘名叫简怀萱？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 394,
      "line_end": 394
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_bo",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳波",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "有是有的……",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 396,
      "line_end": 396
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_bo",
      "text": "现在哪里？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 398,
      "line_end": 398
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_bo",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳波",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "阁下问她做什么？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 400,
      "line_end": 400
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_bo",
      "text": "她是舍妹，被大风暴连着同船桅吹落海中，咱们以为再无生还之望，未想被兄台救起，大恩难谢。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 402,
      "line_end": 403
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_bo",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳波",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "用不着谢，前几日她又跳回海中。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 406,
      "line_end": 406
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_bo",
      "text": "什么……她……跳回海中？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 408,
      "line_end": 408
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_bo",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳波",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "不错，害得咱们白救一场。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 410,
      "line_end": 410
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_long_nian",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳龙年",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你那妹妹也真刚烈，她醒来后不见你们，以为你们全部遭难，说要跟着你们而去！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 412,
      "line_end": 413
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_bo",
      "text": "为什么要让她跳回海中，不能拦她一拦！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 416,
      "line_end": 416
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_bo",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳波",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "奇怪，你妹妹神经不正常要这样做，怪得谁来。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 418,
      "line_end": 418
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_bo",
      "text": "我不相信，她神经不正常决不会无冤无故跳向海中！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 420,
      "line_end": 421
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_long_nian",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳龙年",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你不要怪咱们，事情确是如此，也许你妹妹福星高照，会再有人救起。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 424,
      "line_end": 425
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我不相信，我不相信……",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 428,
      "line_end": 428
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "叶青",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_bo",
      "text": "天下决无一人傻得会自动剧［落海中，要说为了咱们，她并未亲眼见到咱们遭难，就是孩童亦会存着咱们也能生还之望。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 432,
      "line_end": 433
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_bo",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳波",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_long_nian",
      "text": "爹，他们不信算了，快将他们送到陆地，尽了咱们救人救到底的心意。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 436,
      "line_end": 437
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_tai_po",
      "speaker_name": "老太婆",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_long_nian",
      "text": "欧阳龙年，你的护短脾性还没有改啊。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 440,
      "line_end": 440
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_long_nian",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳龙年",
      "listener": "char_lao_tai_po",
      "text": "你是谁？怎知老夫名叫欧阳龙年？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 446,
      "line_end": 446
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_tai_po",
      "speaker_name": "老太婆",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_long_nian",
      "text": "我是谁，我不也是你父子俩救起的灾难人？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 448,
      "line_end": 449
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_long_nian",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳龙年",
      "listener": "char_lao_tai_po",
      "text": "我问你怎会知道老夫的名姓？",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 452,
      "line_end": 452
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_tai_po",
      "speaker_name": "老太婆",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_long_nian",
      "text": "老了，老了，路也走不动了！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 454,
      "line_end": 455
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_bo",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳波",
      "listener": "char_lao_tai_po",
      "text": "装什么蒜，爹问你话快快答来！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 458,
      "line_end": 458
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_tai_po",
      "speaker_name": "老太婆",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_long_nian",
      "text": "龙年兄，你怎把老身忘记了，虽然一别四十余年，老身却还未忘记你呢。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 464,
      "line_end": 465
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_long_nian",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳龙年",
      "listener": "char_lao_tai_po",
      "text": "一别四十余年……",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 468,
      "line_end": 468
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_tai_po",
      "speaker_name": "老太婆",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_long_nian",
      "text": "你想不起吗？哦，我说海龙王你老糊涂了！",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 470,
      "line_end": 470
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_long_nian",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳龙年",
      "listener": "char_lao_tai_po",
      "text": "海龙王这三字老夫早已弃之不用，你到底是谁？",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 472,
      "line_end": 473
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_tai_po",
      "speaker_name": "老太婆",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_long_nian",
      "text": "我知道，我知道……海龙王这三字，我不该再说出，至于我是谁，你既想不起来就当老身是个陌生人。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 476,
      "line_end": 477
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_bo",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳波",
      "listener": "char_lao_tai_po",
      "text": "你既不说，滚回舱去，别站在这里碍眼！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 480,
      "line_end": 480
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_bo",
      "text": "欧阳兄，你不该对老人这般无礼。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 482,
      "line_end": 482
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_bo",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳波",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "要你多管闲事！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 484,
      "line_end": 484
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_tai_po",
      "speaker_name": "老太婆",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_long_nian",
      "text": "龙年兄，你忘了大儿子惨死的教训吗？",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 486,
      "line_end": 487
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_long_nian",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳龙年",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_bo",
      "text": "波儿不得无礼！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 490,
      "line_end": 490
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_bo",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳波",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_long_nian",
      "text": "爹，让孩儿好好教训这小子一顿。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 492,
      "line_end": 492
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_tai_po",
      "speaker_name": "老太婆",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_bo",
      "text": "只怕不是人家的对手……",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 494,
      "line_end": 494
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_bo",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳波",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "十三招要不能将这小子打落海中，枉我爹爹传了十年的武功。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 496,
      "line_end": 497
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_long_nian",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳龙年",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_bo",
      "text": "向这位芮大哥领教可以，不准当真。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 500,
      "line_end": 501
    }
